data.description: Welcome Home!!! This stunning 2-story home is located in the Spring Vistas subdivision located right off 151 and inside of 1604 hwy. Seaworld is just mins away! You can watch the fireworks show from the front of your home! Just picture every holiday event and not needing to drive anywhere to capture this type of firework show. This beautiful home has a lot to offer with a large living area, a formal dining room or second living room space, a breakfast nook, and a spacious kitchen that has an open concept feel. All flooring downstairs has been replaced and updated, along with interior paint. The master bedroom is a grand size room that offers great privacy away from everyone else with a walk-in closet and a separate shower & bathtub. All bedrooms are located upstairs along with a large game room that is perfect for game nights with the family and private space upstairs for the kids as you catch up on your favorite TV shows downstairs. This backyard has an oversized feeling with a shed and a patio slab ready for you to design your choice of covered deck for entertainment and relaxation. The current owner is hoping to rent back the home for a full year and is willing to pay rent!!! So if you are looking for a turn-key investment. This is the One! This comes with residual income and Airbnb opportunities all the way. With its prime location, you'll be minutes away from the best NISD schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment the city has to offer. Don't miss out on the wonderful opportunity to make this gorgeous home yours. Schedule a showing today and call your favorite Realtor!
